Nansha mudi mâyi a bidiila bia ku muelelu kua mâyi ne a misulu mikale mimpe bua mazuwa manene, katuena tumvua bimpe patudi tuenza luendu ne mazuwa makese to.
Mu ditunga dia Finlande, bantu batu banua mazuwa bua kujikija lutetuku, bualu bantu muanda-mutekete anyi muanda-mukulu badi mu mazuwa.
Udi mua kufuanyikija ditunga edi ne dia Norvège, dia Suède ne dia Nouvelle-Zélande, kadi didi bushuwa dia pa buadi (mu ditunga dia Pays-Bas, kudi buatu bumue bua bantu 40).
Mazuwa a bungi a pa buawu a mu ditunga dia Baltique adi enza ngendu mile mu tshimenga tshia Saint-Pétersbourg, mu ditunga dia Russie.
Ebi bidi biumvuija ne: udi mua kupitshisha matuku a bungi mu musoko kampanda muende lumu ne kupingana ne kulala mu buatu butuku abu.
Bua kuya ku muelelu wa mâyi ne mazuwa a pa mâyi kabiena bikengela kuikala ne mukanda wa luendu mushilangane (bu wa mu 2009)
Anu muudi mua kumona mu karte kadi kuulu eku, tshimenga tshia Berlin tshidi kule ne mbuu, nunku kuendakana mu tshimenga etshi ki mbualu bua pa tshibidilu to.
Kuenza luendu ne ndeke kudi mua kutshinyisha bantu ba bidimu bionso ne ba miaba mishilashilangane, nangananga bikalabu kabayi banji kuenza luendu elu anyi bikalabu bapete lutatu lua nunku.
Ki mbualu bua kumvua bundu to: mbualu budi bantu ba bungi batshina ne kabayi banange to.
Bua bakuabu, kumvua bimpe mushindu utu ndeke yenza mudimu ne malu atu enzeka padiye wendesha ndeke kudi mua kubambuluisha bua kutshimuna buôwa budi bufumina ku dipanga kumanya anyi ku dipanga kukanda malu.
Misangu ya bungi, dîba didi ne mushinga wa bungi bua mikanda ya malu a bungenda, bintu anyi biamu bia kulongolola nabi bua kulongolola malu lukasa lukasa.
Mu njila mikuabu, kumpanyi minene ivua ne ndeke yabu, kadi njila mikuabu ne biapu bikese bivua ne lutatu.
Pavuabu batuma bintu ku ndeke, bivua bilomba matuku a bungi bua kufika ku biro bia diumbuka dia bintu mu ditunga ne ku biro bia mbulamatadi.
Pa tshibidilu, mushindu mutambe kupepela wa kubuela mu tshilele etshi ngua kutshiambuila mu tshibombi tshia bintu.
Mushindu mutambe buimpe wa kuenza luendu mu mulongo wa kumpala anyi mu mulongo muibidi ngua kufila makuta a bungi bua kupeta mushindu wa kuenza luendu elu (anyi kulekela kumpanyi webe ukuenzelawu).
Kadi kabiena anu bipepele to: bilondeshile malu akadi menzeke, udi mua kutekemena bua kufuta misangu inayi ya bungi kupita mushinga wa pa tshibidilu ne misangu dikumi ne umue bua muaba wa kumpala.
Mu kuamba kuimpe, kabiena ne mushinga bua kulomba makuta a bungi bua kupeta muaba wa kumpala mu ndeke bua kufika muaba kampanda to.
Bendeshi ba ndeke mbamanye bimpe ne: kudi bantu badi basue kufuta makuta a bungi bua kufika muaba kampanda ne lukasa ne disanka, ne batu bafuta makuta bilondeshile bualu ebu.
Tshimenga tshikulu tshia ditunga dia Moldavie ntshia Chişinău, muakulu wabu wa ku dibele mmuena Roumanie, ne tshiena Russie ke tshidibu bakula bikole.
Mu ditunga dia Moldavie mudi bantu ba bisamba bia bungi, ne mvita ya bisamba mmivulangane mu ditunga edi.
Mu 1994, mvita eyi yakafikisha ku dienza ditunga dia Transnistrie ku est kua ditunga dia Moldavie, didi ne mbulamatadi wadi ne makuta adi kadiyi mamanyike kudi ditunga nansha dimue dia mu ONU.
